      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON CANNES (1) showed good early speed and led throughout to score his maiden two back then finished fifth last start and beaten 10 lengths at Geelong over 400m (23.33). Returns to the course where he won his maiden. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. MR. BILLY LEE (2) is better than last start when fifth (22.70) in a Grade 7 at this track over 390m. Warrants plenty of respect. SHADOW BAND (7) claimed his maiden two back when strongly fancied to break through then fifth last time, beaten 5 lengths (23.66) at Mt Gambier over 400m. Boxed wide here. Expected to do much better this time. PAW XELA (8) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back. Something for the Multiples: GOTHAM SORCERESS (3)",
